tfvars-> env(define kiya, if nhi krte toh variables me jo default diya hai vo use hota, abhi dev diya hai toh dev use hoga)->
->variables.tf (dev hojayega)
->locals.tf (local.env = dev, hoga and based on condition, machine_type= e2medium hojayge)
->main.tf (isme jo resource create hoga vo name= demo-vm-dev name se create hoga, machine-type= e2-medium)
Locals ke use 

terraform.tfvars(env define)->variable.tf(get to know abt env)-> locals.tf(local.env=dev, and machine type based on it)->
->provider.tf(google api se connect) ->main.tf(vm create)